(SKILL.md) without a code change / redeploy. Design (decided via brainstorm,
captured in docs/TODO.md): built-in skills stay baked & read-only; user
skills live under the persisted workspace/ volume and override built-ins by
name (survive Docker rebuilds; "mine" vs "shipped" stay separate).

